  "text": "The rate of the communication in transition [T3] is specified in the fifth component of definition [CITATION_1] . Notice that the process inside box E is not changed by [T3] because the guarded replication operator rep allows to regenerate output x !(sig ) each time it is consumed. The process ch(x, IdP ) into box S changes the type of the interaction site x : IdS from IdS to IdP , completing the transformation from substrate S to product P, described by transition [T4]:",
